# Wedding Hall — monorepo overview

Wedding-budget **MVP** (Phase 1): email/password auth, onboarding wizard, venue estimate dashboard.

## Packages
- **`client/`** — Vite + React 19 + TypeScript + Tailwind. SPA with React Router. Supabase JS in the browser (anon key + RLS).
- **`server/`** — Next.js 15 (App Router), minimal: `GET /api/health` + room to grow.
- **`supabase/`** — Postgres schema + RLS + seed (`schema.sql`, `seed.sql`).

## Docs (read first)
- @PLAN.md — scope
- @RULES.md — binding rules
- @README.md — setup, env, deploy, Supabase URLs
- @AGENTS.md — agent orientation + skill link

## Root scripts
From repo root: `npm run dev:client` · `npm run dev:server` · `npm run lint` · `npm run build`

## Deploy model
- Production **client**: branch **`master-client`** (or Vercel project root `client`).
- Production **server**: branch **`master-server`** (or Vercel project root `server`).
- Integration: **`main`** / **`master`** + `ci.yml` (lint + build, no deploy).
